{"tid":550840,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"本癲狗斬撚死你!","createTime":"2018-02-05T06:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T07:53:27.000Z","uid":74981,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7f5ce00af00cee4f9cbaf54d038873fd0f1ae139","tid":550840,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T06:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1971a5adad805bfafd8d4b1f9446993e0a0b5dd5","tid":550840,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5d1d3b7201fdd653817a4263eb1d0041ab75197","tid":550840,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e05fea5e36f4098e56672006244a02baaeb08c","tid":550840,"uid":74981,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">肥鳩大隻乃連登論壇知名柒頭，經常誣衊本癲狗借佢條傻鳩上位，點知當佢同本癲狗正面交鋒就高下立見，廢物現形，睇下各位撐邊個多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/87fkcxet3j/1508057207119.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F87fkcxet3j%2F1508057207119.png&h=76fb8ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">咦? 肥鳩大隻，你想借本癲狗上位失敗wo，睇下我同你個post分別既支持度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上唔到位發爛咋呀傻鳩</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>再睇下你條本癲狗交鋒之下係輸得幾咁羞家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/5f5hw5g2un/1508057486497.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F5f5hw5g2un%2F1508057486497.png&h=c92bb693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/zzu52bwmn/1508057435505.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2Fzzu52bwmn%2F1508057435505.png&h=f091cd9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由此可見，肥鳩大隻同本癲狗實力縣殊，想借本癲狗上位卻慘敗收場，因而只能作出零星而無力的反抗，反過來誣衊本癲狗借佢條傻鳩上位，其實本癲狗只係從容撚狗，已獲得大家支持</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>同時亦證明左，無論肥鳩大隻花盡心機，唸盡辦法想同本癲狗玩，但換黎既結果只有慘敗同被撚，所以永遠活係本癲狗既陰影之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ce74705f9a6ff371fdc134a8b25736f224e1044d","tid":550840,"uid":74981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>肥絲大隻，柒人柒事，2018第一炮之小丑娛賓</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">話說有巴打問有冇人去過&ldquo;好景4樓有4級&rdquo;，肥鳩大隻自以為聰明，串人應該講4仔，唔係講4級，講4級即係大陸人:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/e2riv8we9/1516170512090.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fe2riv8we9%2F1516170512090.png&h=d7707279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">點知有巴打出埋片，證明本地呀叔係會講4樓有4級，用&ldquo;4級&rdquo;哩個叫法並唔係等如大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/b7j12fuq9/1516170653731.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fb7j12fuq9%2F1516170653731.png&h=2835cfe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>肥絲大隻頓時柒到貼地，啞口無言，落荒而逃，狼狽至極，但卻避免不了各位巴打爭相繼續對其恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/3rjrgv4ip/1516170812853.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2F3rjrgv4ip%2F1516170812853.png&h=eecc38a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/9shgdz1fl/1516171086724.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2F9shgdz1fl%2F1516171086724.png&h=1daab7aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/4ichm3wg1/1516171151944.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2F4ichm3wg1%2F1516171151944.png&h=02ab2e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/jr2ezyq5d/1516171268632.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fjr2ezyq5d%2F1516171268632.png&h=0a9a6f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/5xe2b2pw1/1516171326975.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2F5xe2b2pw1%2F1516171326975.png&h=ed2675fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>溫馨提示: 肥絲大隻其實你咁撚柒，不如開post或者留comment之前，咨詢一下你老母既意見先，咁會減少好多被人恥笑既機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"06a171cd9bf77f59d1882049cbbf73c72408a356","tid":550840,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f712e2a6b04621e654dfbe1692dec46b8f7b483f","tid":550840,"uid":38820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T06:36:25.000Z","msg":"G持樓主"},{"pid":"6f325948afd0dc14a068b52dafd2f87f221a68e1","tid":550840,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f712e2a6b04621e65